    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels under the MRL 2 credibility matrix for a Class II device at Medium model influence. The six not-assessed factors are consistent with MRL 2 scoping. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The relative hemolysis index predictions satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion against the predicate device at all five operating points.",
